{"tid":756774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸「奶茶妹」富豪老公劉強東捲入澳洲強姦案 驚傳豪宅派對男賓客性侵女𡃁模","createTime":"2018-07-26T09:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T10:37:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a8efebf1d2b98c3e84b3948012cd1eab42624507","tid":756774,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpvOiand.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpvOiand.jpg&h=324e3211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">劉強東（右）與太太「奶茶妹」。（翻攝自Instagram）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國網路紅人「奶茶妹」章澤天老公、中國電商巨頭京東總裁劉強東被捲入性侵案中，外媒指出，這起案件發生在2015年，劉強東在澳洲雪梨辦派對，派對上有男賓客性侵女模，劉強東則沒有被指控任何違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報中文網》報導，劉強東於2015年在雪梨舉辦豪奢派對，一名房地產開發商徐龍偉(Longwei Xu）是受邀賓客，徐男在派對中對一名女模灌酒，並將她帶到飯店房間性侵。當地時間週一，法院判徐男包括未經原告同意發生性關係等7項罪名成立，劉強東則與此案無關。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，劉強東曾以案件可能損害他的婚姻與生意為由，希望法院不公布他的姓名，但法官拒絕此請求，當地媒體於本週一公布其姓名。報導分析，這意味著中國商界巨頭不希望讓外人知道他們的奢華生活。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2498873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2498873&d=MS5Lvb1G68LAnWEss6f3JQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ed6ec508\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2498873&h=b704c7b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2498873</a>"},{"pid":"d053f763988799d72452c742e31ff721841cbe30","tid":756774,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"好出奇呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c08586d2ea14ceac8a995e00448b7d634d5d84a","tid":756774,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco